足性幻想（sexual fantasy），其後再肢解對方軀體。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬德森的辯護律師引述當事人指，該工作室容許多人自由出入，甚至有實習生居住；工作室內的硬碟機非由他擁有。</span><br />\n<br />\n警方繼續調查，而疑兇馬德森的拘留期則延長至本月 31 日。</blockquote><br />\n證據確鑿，個律師都仲可以講d咁既野，唉</blockquote><br />\n佢職責黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c63ce492851bf47b2cb69012801960dbdd2d48e","tid":423812,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遭活生生斬頭，或勒死。<br />\n<br />\n斬完頭又勒死？<br />\n利申：閱讀理解零分嘅弱智</blockquote><br />\nOr啊 唔係and啊<br />\n柒唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同時有斬頭同勒頸片段，法醫仲未驗到佢真正致死嘅原因，所以斬頭同勒死都有可能係致死原因。"},{"pid":"70f40073eeb1c4012467f3ae5efb86bafea3d792","tid":423812,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280ab951e10fbbd4acf8870a0a89a75829f7954f","tid":423812,"uid":34010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n證據確鑿，個律師都仲可以講d咁既野，唉</blockquote><br />\n點為之證據確鑿？已經排除晒其餘全部可能？"},{"pid":"607326087b655a201f8ef59d8f349920ffa764a5","tid":423812,"uid":16150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"呢d 人可唔可以調番轉施番落佢身上？<br />\n你支解人就得<br />\n人支解你得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e53b52cff5632e90c57e1bb0cf3efae32bd492","tid":423812,"uid":70946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"活生生斬人個頭都會性興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢條友真係留不得，必須死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39878e935eee6a860fac175f8f271e63aa839e9a","tid":423812,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"咁老都吼 以為House of cards  Mattie咁<